Creeps Characteristics
	Creep - Units
		Creeps live for 30-60minutes
		Each creep has a max of 50 available body part slots
		Each body part has weight, affecting movement


	Creep Body Part List
		Carry - transfer energy (50)
		Work - harvest energy, construct and repair structures, upgrade controllers (100)
		Attack - ability of short-range attack (80)
		Ranged Attack -range attacks (150)
		Move - ability to move (50)
		heal - heal units (250)
		Claim - control territory (600)
		Tough - defense (10)

	Creep Body Part
		100 hits per body part
		Order in which created , will be destroyed

	Creep Boost
		Boosting requires 30 mineral compound and 20 energy units
